<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Closes Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, July 6 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at Tehran
Stock Exchange on Tuesday closed at 1,729.46 points, up 1.13
points from Monday's finish.
</P>
<P>
A total of 2,243,068 shares changed hands in 1,282 turns and
the turnover stood at 9.5 billion rials (about 3.16 million
dollars).
</P>
<P>
The shares of 25 companies made gains while those of 17 others
declined. 
</P>
