and swore an oath one by one.
</P>
<P>
The approval has been assured of after Barak managed to put
together a seven-faction coalition controlling 75 seats in the
120-member Knesset, which has 15 factions.
</P>
<P>
While presenting his government to the Knesset earlier, Barak
pledged to revive the peace process on all fronts, giving same
priorities to the Palestinian, Syrian and Lebanese tracks.
