<HEADLINE> Tanzania Follows Closely with China's Reform </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DAR ES SALAAM, July 6 (Xinhua) -- Tanzanian President Benjamin
Mkapa said Tuesday that his country has followed closely with the
experiences of China's economic reforms.
</P>
