<TEXT>
<P>
"We greatly welcome (the new government) of Prime Minister
Barak who is trying to deal smoothly with political issues" in the
Mideast peace process while "working on domestic integrity,"
Japanese Foreign Minister Masahiko Komura said in a statement
Wednesday.
</P>
