<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks dropped 115.17
points or 0.8 percent Wednesday with the Hang Seng Index closed at
14,257.44 points.
</P>
<P>
The market turnover, however, increased by 4.546 billion HK
dollars (583 million U.S. dollars) to hit 16.548 billion HK
dollars (2.121 billion U.S. dollars) Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
