<HEADLINE> Two International High-Tech Fairs In Southern Chinese City </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Two international fairs dealing
with automation and water treatment opened today in the capital of
China's Guangdong Province.
</P>
