Technology Fair, Chinese and overseas specialists will discuss the
city's high-tech development project for sewage treatment, which
is expected to cost 20 billion yuan (2.4 billion US dollars).
</P>
<P>
The fairs are being sponsored by the Scientific and
Technological Association of Guangdong Province.  
