<HEADLINE> Kuwait Stock Exchange Index Closes Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUWAIT CITY, July 7 (Xinhua) -- Kuwait Stock Exchange index
closed at 1,587.8 points Wednesday, up 4.9 points from Tuesday's
finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 10.72 million Kuwaiti dinars (35.37 million
U.S. dollars) as 35.08 million shares were traded in 785
deals. 
