would continue to create an enabling environment for all citizens
to participate in the shaping of the economy, she said.
</P>
<P>
According to Chitauro, the success of the Zimbabwe Program for
Economic and Social Transformation (Zimperest) hinged on
cooperation among all stakeholders in the economy.
</P>
<P>
Zimperest aims to bring adequate and sustainable rate of
economic growth and social development, reduce poverty and create
productive employment. 
